snippet.title: Nine Years of Shadows Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2021
snippet.description: Here's some gameplay from Nine Years of Shadows, a moving Metroidvania with a soundtrack from the composers behind Mega Man, Castlevania and Metal Gear. Keep your eye on this one, as it's coming soon.
